snippet.title: The Darkest Files - Gameplay Trailer December 2023
snippet.description:
"The Darkest Files" is a playable historical True Crime thriller. 
You take the role of young prosecutor Esther Katz in Frankfurt, Germany 1956. Your job is to solve cold cases that took place before the war and dive into the Darkest of Times. 
Support the game and gain aaccess to Early Birt Tiers to sign up for our upcoming Kickstarter at 
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/paintbucketgames/the-darkest-files
